{"id":218,"date":"2018-07-20T07:52:52","date_gmt":"2018-07-20T07:52:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/aquentro\/?p=218"},"modified":"2018-07-23T14:26:46","modified_gmt":"2018-07-23T14:26:46","slug":"benefits-of-short-term-business-rentals-over-hotels","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/aquentro\/2018\/07\/20\/benefits-of-short-term-business-rentals-over-hotels\/","title":{"rendered":"Benefits of Short-Term Business Rentals over Hotels"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Everybody knows that traveling double occupancy is more cost-savvy. When travelling with someone, sharing a room will be cheaper than booking two separate rooms. If you are travelling in business with someone, we will host you at the best place in the city.To many business travelers, the idea of not staying at a hotel could be considered heretical. The predictability of hotels makes them look solid.<\/p>\n<p><!--more--><\/p>\n<p><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"42\" data-permalink=\"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/aquentro\/home\/depositphotos_89497476_original\/\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/aquentro\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/20\/2018\/07\/Depositphotos_89497476_original.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2560,960\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Depositphotos_89497476_original\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https:\/\/themes.getmotopress.com\/aquentro\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/20\/2018\/07\/Depositphotos_89497476_original-300x113.jpg\" data-large-file=